<A>__{action as per voice over.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{how have we had the best blood, and the brightest eyes, too, of europe throbbing round the table as i and the chevalier have held the cards and the bank against some terrible player, who was matching some thousands out of his millions against our all which was there on the baize!}
<L>__{interior gaming room germany night}
<A>__{roderick dealing a faro bank.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{our principles were: play grandly, honorably. be not, of course, cast down at losing; but, above all, be not eager at winning, as mean souls are.}
